contact_tracing: SCDHEC is responsible for the process of contact tracing. USCB’s Public Health Response Team has completed contact-tracing training through the Johns Hopkins University and will support SCDHEC to implement contact tracing and additive practices, e.g. verification of student class attendance, seating charts, student ID swipes, and portable swipes at student events.
self_reporting: please complete the Student Report Form, so that The Public Health Response Team can assist you
